title: No more Leases or Rent Increases! Invest in your OWN HOME!
posting_body: ["It's time to stop paying rent and invest in", 'YOUR VERY OWN HOME!', 'We have just the home for you', "and it's only", '$1809/mo!*', 'Thousands in upgraded features included at no extra charge!', 'We simplified the process just for you.', 'From writing the contract to closing and getting your keys, everything is done onsite!', 'Not only that, we pay your closing costs when you finance with our approved Lender!', 'We are here for you!', 'Call TODAY for more info!', 'show contact info', 'x 300', 'The Allatoona Plan:', '🗝3 bedrooms', '🗝2 full bathrooms', '🗝Full Whirlpool Kitchen Appliance Suite', '🗝Walk in closet in the master bedroom', '🗝One Level - Open Concept', '🗝BRAND NEW CONSTRUCTION', '🗝Professionally Landscaped Yard', 'Click or call today!', 'show contact info', 'x 300', '*P&I.', 'Price $319,900, 5.625% Fixed/6.717% APR, 3.5% Down, FHA 30 Year, OAC from third party lender.', 'Other fees such as taxes, insurance, and HOA are not included in the sample monthly payment amount.', 'Prices and rates subject to change without notice.']
